    "text": "Question 1\nUse a foreach loop to repeat 100 times:\ngenerate a random sample from an exponential distribution with mean 1\ncalculate mean and variance\nrow-bind your results (rbind) (results = mean and variance).",
    "crumbs": [
      "<span class='chapter-number'>2</span>  <span class='chapter-title'>Prac day 12</span>"
    ]
  },
  {
    "objectID": "Day 12 Practical.html#question-1",
    "href": "Day 12 Practical.html#question-1",
    "title": "Prac day 12",
    "section": "",
    "text": "Answer\n\n#creates a column vector of all the means and variances for each 100 values sampled from an exponential distribution with mean 1 for each iteration\nresult =  foreach(i = 1:100, .combine = \"rbind\") %do%{\n   exp_vec = rexp(100, 1)\n   mean = mean(exp_vec)\n   var = var(exp_vec)\n   c(round(mean,2),round(var,2)) \n}\n# changes the column and row names\ncolnames(result) &lt;- c(\"Mean\", \"Variance\")\nrownames(result) &lt;- c(seq(1,100))\n\n#Put output into a table using kable\nkable(result, caption = \"Table 1 : Means and Variances for 100 exponential distributions with mean 1\") %&gt;% \n  kable_styling(bootstrap_options = \"striped\", \"hover\") %&gt;% \n  scroll_box(., height = \"300px\")\n\n\n\nTable 1 : Means and Variances for 100 exponential distributions with mean 1\n\n\nMean\nVariance\n\n\n\n\n1.02\n0.77\n\n\n1.09\n0.98\n\n\n0.83\n0.84\n\n\n0.96\n0.84\n\n\n0.83\n0.74\n\n\n1.00\n0.74\n\n\n0.98\n0.96\n\n\n0.93\n0.93\n\n\n0.97\n1.17\n\n\n1.03\n1.05\n\n\n0.91\n0.62\n\n\n1.01\n0.81\n\n\n0.87\n0.85\n\n\n0.84\n0.62\n\n\n1.04\n0.80\n\n\n1.00\n0.80\n\n\n1.17\n1.55\n\n\n0.88\n0.71\n\n\n1.00\n0.88\n\n\n0.93\n0.70\n\n\n1.05\n0.73\n\n\n0.93\n1.13\n\n\n0.99\n0.84\n\n\n1.07\n1.25\n\n\n1.00\n1.11\n\n\n0.97\n0.90\n\n\n0.90\n1.10\n\n\n1.05\n0.91\n\n\n1.02\n0.83\n\n\n1.13\n1.53\n\n\n0.97\n0.87\n\n\n0.92\n0.63\n\n\n1.01\n0.79\n\n\n1.01\n0.85\n\n\n0.90\n0.54\n\n\n0.96\n1.43\n\n\n1.02\n0.84\n\n\n1.00\n0.98\n\n\n0.83\n0.58\n\n\n0.95\n1.12\n\n\n0.90\n0.90\n\n\n0.81\n0.52\n\n\n0.95\n0.77\n\n\n0.86\n0.71\n\n\n0.85\n0.81\n\n\n1.07\n0.94\n\n\n1.02\n0.94\n\n\n1.01\n0.80\n\n\n0.91\n1.11\n\n\n1.03\n1.34\n\n\n1.07\n0.72\n\n\n1.00\n0.79\n\n\n1.23\n1.58\n\n\n1.17\n1.00\n\n\n0.93\n1.07\n\n\n1.13\n1.29\n\n\n1.07\n0.83\n\n\n0.88\n0.67\n\n\n1.05\n1.10\n\n\n0.96\n0.79\n\n\n0.85\n0.76\n\n\n0.83\n0.76\n\n\n1.01\n1.06\n\n\n0.93\n1.04\n\n\n0.98\n0.73\n\n\n0.97\n1.04\n\n\n1.00\n1.27\n\n\n1.09\n1.46\n\n\n1.00\n2.05\n\n\n0.92\n0.73\n\n\n1.00\n1.52\n\n\n0.97\n0.53\n\n\n0.94\n0.95