    "text": "Question 2\nUse the doParallel package and foreach to bootstrap the median for the galaxies data (in library MASS).\n\nAnswer\n\nset.seed(123)\nc1 &lt;- makeCluster(2) # assigned 2 workes to the task \nregisterDoParallel(c1)\n# gives time output of how long it will take both workers to create a vector with the boostrapped values\nsystem.time({median_estimate &lt;- median(galaxies)\n  boostrap &lt;- foreach(i =  1:1000, .combine = 'rbind', .packages = 'MASS') %dopar%{\n    cases = sample(galaxies, size = 82, replace = T)\n    median = median(cases)\n    c(median)\n}}) \n\n   user  system elapsed \n   0.40    0.05    0.60 \n\nstopCluster(c1)\ncolnames(boostrap) &lt;- c(\"Boostrap Median\")\nrownames(boostrap) &lt;- c(seq(1,1000))\nboostrap %&gt;% \n  kable() %&gt;% \n  kable_styling(bootstrap_options = \"striped\", \"hover\", full_width = FALSE) %&gt;% \n  scroll_box(., height = \"300px\")\n\n\n\n\n\nBoostrap Median\n\n\n\n\n21701.0\n\n\n20208.5\n\n\n21314.5\n\n\n20875.0\n\n\n20986.0\n\n\n20860.5\n\n\n20218.0\n\n\n20986.0\n\n\n21137.0\n\n\n21314.5\n\n\n20415.0\n\n\n20629.0\n\n\n20821.0\n\n\n21137.0\n\n\n20808.0\n\n\n20820.5\n\n\n20930.5\n\n\n21757.5\n\n\n20172.5\n\n\n21314.5\n\n\n20795.0\n\n\n21061.5\n\n\n20205.5\n\n\n20835.0\n\n\n20795.0\n\n\n21596.5\n\n\n20821.0\n\n\n20221.0\n\n\n20860.5\n\n\n20712.0\n\n\n20415.0\n\n\n20218.0\n\n\n20930.5\n\n\n20916.0\n\n\n20808.0\n\n\n20508.0\n\n\n20986.0\n\n\n21061.5\n\n\n20629.0\n\n\n21137.0\n\n\n20875.0\n\n\n21061.5\n\n\n21701.0\n\n\n20196.0\n\n\n20215.0\n\n\n22197.0\n\n\n20808.0\n\n\n20725.0\n\n\n20196.0\n\n\n21701.0\n\n\n21061.5\n\n\n20318.0\n\n\n20875.0\n\n\n20605.0\n\n\n21757.5\n\n\n21653.0\n\n\n20808.0\n\n\n21314.5\n\n\n20930.5\n\n\n20860.5\n\n\n20795.0\n\n\n20860.5\n\n\n20848.0\n\n\n20629.0\n\n\n20846.0\n\n\n20821.0\n\n\n20846.0\n\n\n20860.5\n\n\n21475.5\n\n\n21726.0\n\n\n20196.0\n\n\n20833.5\n\n\n20846.0\n\n\n20215.0\n\n\n20712.0\n\n\n21343.5\n\n\n21867.5\n\n\n21757.5\n\n\n20215.0\n\n\n21867.5\n\n\n20821.0\n\